														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4717695">
									

<p>The first section was great, but everything else suffered from one major problem: it's written in the wrong POV. Why is this written from the Foundation's perspective? They aren't really mentioned anywhere else in the series besides one occurrence in The Years Between. So all of these characters are introduced and then just tossed aside. And since the Foundation never really reappears in this series&#8230; why not just have it written from Tim's perspective? That would give a lot more of an emotional punch to everything, seeing his town get shut down and investigated.</p>
<p>-1.</p>

